    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Grid convergence index < 2% on RH index. Validation MAE of 6.3% is well within the 15% acceptance threshold. The uncertainty quantification campaign (512 LHS runs, Sobol indices computed) confirms that RH remains below 1.0 across the 95th percentile of the parameter space, providing additional confidence beyond the point-estimate validation. Six factors not assessed are consistent with MRL 2 scoping and are individually justified. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
